invalid type: string "Under 180 days:\nMedical examination form for short-term students\nOver 180 days:\nHealth Certificate for Residence Application\nThe list of authorized hospitals overseas:\nhttps://www.cdc.gov.tw/En/Category/ListContent/C4w0xUaCBCKzdd6BxDGWcA?uaid=hyLQahxQbQVM1NEt-Bbe1Q\n*The certification should be provided before your arrival to Taiwan (Valid for 3 months only).\nNotices:\n